{"tid":1395060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳遊行批左但有點擔心","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T02:14:23.000Z","uid":236646,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"2c163c646a7c9b296cc5e2e1290b455b49562a3b","tid":1395060,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"今次批左個遊行....但係唔知黑、警想點對遊行人士<br />\n會唔會又係有黑勢力一齊想夾人...<br />\n定係真係好似班人咁講準備漒水彈黎攻擊市民?<br />\n大家要注意一下安全...以免比人攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做好保護措施<br />\n<br />\n由元朗...去到天水圍....去到上環<br />\n警察已經癲晒...佢地已經唔會阻止黑社會做任何野<br />\n可以任由元朗白衫打人...天水圍放煙花攻擊人<br />\n完全無任何行動...由得市民比人攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到到今日警察已經信唔過<br />\n大家要學識保護自己<br />\n<br />\n希望大家平安<br />\n警察所作所為...個天一定會收佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb349edf0052443ca0f6c9dd9ad5fb539d242691","tid":1395060,"uid":60129,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"做好本分啦<br />\n我相信如果警察唔出手阻撓我地嘅話，我哋喺將軍澳都冇乜衝擊目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通真係係有衝唔係又衝，真真正正影響當地居民咩"},{"pid":"2f117e7ac2c33d9dd32574ac8b58ddf085431844","tid":1395060,"uid":265662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"人多就安全"},{"pid":"273455c3f023add485f9f6ac7a43c3155f3fa88c","tid":1395060,"uid":219194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:40:11.000Z","msg":"定啲黎啦 相信自己 相信前線"},{"pid":"dabb04ebc20249d683ea0f3e4bb15219853f7241","tid":1395060,"uid":169771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2633e5c13820808083ab8278a237f02a8d676b25","tid":1395060,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"各位手足要做好安全措施..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632dab3694cf71112507fcbd658bf922904a8395","tid":1395060,"uid":258770,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"去將軍澳原本既主因係因為不滿CCTVB報假新聞<br />\n如果行動升級就自然會去搞CCTVB, 不過佢地位於工業邨<br />\n只有一條路出入, 加上入面毫無補給, 得一個公廁, 最多比埋你入去壹傳媒借廁所借水<br />\n以一向既佔路磨爛蓆抗爭模式黎玩係必死無疑 所以公安係唔會擔心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fae0382ee979623fdfb3f8a5ce5684efdeb392","tid":1395060,"uid":89184,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f8d82b56ecc681fda56fcc3276cfad5f7d954e","tid":1395060,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb349edf0052443ca0f6c9dd9ad5fb539d242691","tid":1395060,"uid":60129,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"做好本分啦<br />\n我相信如果警察唔出手阻撓我地嘅話，我哋喺將軍澳都冇乜衝擊目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通真係係有衝唔係又衝，真真正正影響當地居民咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"TVB?"},{"pid":"e463e3e002ab1b3e418c6bd2e680a3b322034170","tid":1395060,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n黑警批遊行 係咪有陰謀<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><br />\n<code>「然遍地腥羶，滿街狼犬！」「吾今日死無餘憾，</code><br />\n<code>國事成不成，自有同志者在。」 - 林覺民 1911</code><br />\n<code>「我哋係前世做錯事 所以今世要搞革命！」</code><br />\n<code>- 無名 2019</code></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>明之子  奮起之<span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span>赴抗暴   驍勇世<span style=\"color: gold;\">代</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span>城安<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7qZ3RL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/